# Phase 4 — Kubernetes manifests

Namespace: `qr-app` (proposed)

Will contain:
- `namespace.yaml`
- `api.yaml` (Deployment, Service, Secret/ExternalSecret, PDB)
- `frontend.yaml` (Deployment, Service, ConfigMap)
- `ingress.yaml` (NGINX Ingress, TLS via cert-manager)

Validate locally with: `kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f k8s/`
